               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dāwit “Psalter” (fols. 2r-181rb)
 I-1) Mazmura Dāwit “Psalms of
                     David” (fols. 2r-142v) 
 I-2) Maḥālǝya nabiyāt “The Canticles of the
                     Prophets” (fols. 142v-157v) 
 I-3) Maḥālǝya maḥālǝy “Song of Songs” (fols.
                     157v-166r) 
 I-4) Wǝddāse Māryām “Praise of Mary” (fols. 166ra-176vb) 
                     I-5) ʾAnqaṣa bǝrhān “The Gate of Light” (fols. 176vb-181rb)
 
 Additio
                     1.</summary>
