                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra (name of St Mary in Texts I-4, I-5);
                           titles and numbers of the Pss. and Canticles; numbers of Songs; title of
                           Texts I-2, I-3; title and incipit of the daily readings of Text I-4;
                           title of Text I-5; name of the Hebrew letters in Ps. 118; doxology at the
                           end of each Song; elements of the punctuation signs.
 A few lines
                           (alternating with black lines) on the incipit page of Texts I-1 and
                           I-5.</seg>
